_sText:
Minecraft! now in CS!
Now it's your chance to play Minecraft.. with guns

After explored hours of minecraft world, I came out with this minecraft map.

You can dig DIRT, GRAVEL, COBBLESTONE with your KNIFE.
Yes, I have to let you know that this map is different from others, because you can actually break blocks. They are not just useless breakable stuffs. You can only break them with your KNIFE!

this map is a beta and a cut version. Because of some engine overload issues, I have to remove the block gibs and red-stone powder effects.
